<div class="m392fn" style="padding:24px 28px;max-width:920px;font-family:inherit;color:#2c2e3a;">
  <style>
    .m392fn h2{margin:0 0 4px;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;}
    .m392fn .sub{color:#6b7280;margin:0 0 4px;}
    .m392fn .note{color:#9aa1ad;font-size:12.5px;margin:0 0 18px;}
    .m392fn .sk{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6e8ee;border-radius:10px;padding:8px 6px 4px;}
    .m392fn svg text{font-family:inherit;}
    .m392fn table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;margin-top:20px;}
    .m392fn th{text-align:right;color:#8a93a3;font-weight:600;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.04em;
      text-transform:uppercase;padding:9px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #eef0f4;white-space:nowrap;}
    .m392fn th.l,.m392fn td.l{text-align:left;}
    .m392fn td{text-align:right;padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f3f7;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;}
    .m392fn td code{background:#f1f3f7;color:#475569;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:5px;font-size:12px;}
    .m392fn .num{flex:none;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;color:#fff;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-right:8px;vertical-align:middle;}
    .m392fn .drop{color:#e2574c;}
    .m392fn .foot{color:#9aa1ad;font-size:12px;margin-top:18px;line-height:1.6;}
  </style>

  {% set colors = ['#2f6bff', '#3a86c8', '#3aa0a8', '#f59e0b'] %}

  <h2>Conversion-Trichter (Sankey)</h2>
  <p class="sub">Klassischer E-Commerce-Funnel &middot; {{ prettyDate }}</p>
  <p class="note">Jeder Block ist eine konkrete Shop-Seite. Die <strong>Bandbreite</strong> zeigt den Fluss
    der Besuche; bei jedem Schritt zweigt der <strong>Abbruch</strong> (rot) nach unten ab.</p>

  <div class="sk">
    <svg width="100%" viewBox="0 0 {{ sankey.w }} {{ sankey.h }}" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" role="img">
      <!-- Abbruch-Bänder (rot) -->
      {% for f in sankey.drop %}
        <path d="{{ f.d }}" fill="#ef4444" fill-opacity="0.28"><title>Abbruch: {{ f.count }} ({{ f.pct }} %)</title></path>
        <text x="{{ f.mx }}" y="{{ f.my }}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11.5" fill="#e2574c" font-weight="600">&#8595; {{ f.count|number_format(0, ',', '.') }}</text>
        <text x="{{ f.mx }}" y="{{ f.my + 14 }}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10.5" fill="#9aa1ad">Abbruch {{ f.pct }} %</text>
      {% endfor %}
      <!-- weiter-Bänder (blau) -->
      {% for f in sankey.go %}
        <path d="{{ f.d }}" fill="#2f6bff" fill-opacity="0.18"><title>weiter: {{ f.count }} ({{ f.pct }} %)</title></path>
      {% endfor %}
      <!-- Knoten (Stufen) -->
      {% for nd in sankey.nodes %}
        <rect x="{{ nd.x }}" y="{{ nd.y }}" width="{{ nd.w }}" height="{{ nd.h }}" rx="4" fill="{{ colors[loop.index0] }}">
          <title>{{ loop.index }}. {{ nd.label }} — {{ nd.count }} ({{ nd.pct_total }} % vom Start)</title>
        </rect>
        <text x="{{ nd.cx }}" y="20" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12.5" font-weight="700" fill="#2c2e3a">{{ loop.index }}. {{ nd.label }}</text>
        <text x="{{ nd.cx }}" y="{{ sankey.topPad + nd.h + 16 }}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="{{ colors[loop.index0] }}">{{ nd.count|number_format(0, ',', '.') }}</text>
        <text x="{{ nd.cx }}" y="{{ sankey.topPad + nd.h + 30 }}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10.5" fill="#9aa1ad">{{ nd.pct_total }} %</text>
      {% endfor %}
    </svg>
  </div>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th class="l">Schritt</th><th class="l">WordPress-Seite</th><th>Besuche</th><th>% vom Start</th><th>weiter</th><th>Abbruch</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for s in steps %}
        <tr>
          <td class="l"><span class="num" style="background:{{ colors[loop.index0] }}">{{ loop.index }}</span><strong>{{ s.label }}</strong></td>
          <td class="l">{{ s.page }} <code>{{ s.path }}</code></td>
          <td>{{ s.count|number_format(0, ',', '.') }}</td>
          <td>{{ s.pct_total }} %</td>
          <td>{% if loop.first %}&mdash;{% else %}{{ s.pct_step }} %{% endif %}</td>
          <td class="drop">{% if loop.first %}&mdash;{% else %}{{ s.drop_abs|number_format(0, ',', '.') }} ({{ s.dropoff }} %){% endif %}</td>
        </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p class="foot">
    <strong>Datenquelle:</strong> die vier URL-Ziele „Funnel-1 &hellip; 4" (Menü <em>Ziele</em>) &mdash; je ein
    Seitenaufruf der oben genannten Shop-Seiten.<br>
    <strong>A/B-Vergleich:</strong> oben rechts das Segment „AB-Variante" (Original / Shop-Variante) hinzufügen.
  </p>
</div>
